The schema describes configuration for a Grunt task. It is an object type. It defines several reusable components under 'definitions': 'dynamic' is an object with properties : 'expand' which is a boolean with a default of false, 'cwd' which is a string, 'dest' which is a string, 'ext' which is a string, 'extDot' which is an enum with allowed values 'first' and 'last', defaulting to 'first', 'filter' is an enum with allowed values 'isFile', 'isDirectory', 'isBlockDevice', 'isCharacterDevice', 'isSymbolicLink', 'isFIFO', 'isSocket', 'flatten' is a boolean defaulting to false, 'matchBase' is a boolean defaulting to false, 'nonull' is a boolean defaulting to false, 'rename' is a string and 'src' which is a required array of strings that must contain at least one unique item .碚
